<h3>Generator Options</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>--stimulus</code>: Generates a new Stimulus controller named nav_controller.js and registers it for enhanced mobile menu functionality</li>
  <li><code>--directory</code>: Customize the component location (defaults to <code>app/views/rui/components</code>)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Component Properties</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>logo</code>: Logo content - accepts image tags, inline SVG, or plain text (String or HTML, required)</li>
  <li><code>controller</code>: Stimulus controller name for mobile menu functionality (String, default: "nav")</li>
  <li><code>classes</code>: Additional CSS classes for the outer header element (String, optional)</li>
  <li><code>content</code>: Custom navigation content to replace default left/right subcomponents (String or block, optional)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Subcomponents</h3>

<p>The navigation component includes two optional subcomponents that can be customized. These subcomponents now support both default content and custom block content:</p>

<ul>
  <li><code>navigation/left</code>: Left-side navigation links
    <ul>
      <li>Default: Renders placeholder menu items</li>
      <li>With block: Accepts custom content for left navigation</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code>navigation/right</code>: Right-side navigation links
    <ul>
      <li>Default: Renders Login/Sign Up buttons</li>
      <li>With block: Accepts custom content for right navigation</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3>Usage Patterns</h3>

<p>The navigation component supports three levels of customization:</p>

<ol>
  <li><strong>Default subcomponents:</strong> Use built-in left/right navigation with default content</li>
  <li><strong>Custom subcomponent blocks:</strong> Override individual left/right sections while maintaining structure</li>
  <li><strong>Complete override:</strong> Replace entire navigation content with custom block</li>
</ol>

<div class="not-prose">
<% content_for :erb, flush: true do %>
<!-- Pattern 1: Default subcomponents -->
<%%= rui :navigation, logo: image_tag("logo.png") %>

<!-- Pattern 2: Custom subcomponent blocks -->
<%%= rui :navigation, logo: content_tag(:span, "Brand") do %>
  <%%= rui "navigation/left" do %>
    <!-- Custom left navigation -->
  <%% end %>
  <%%= rui "navigation/right" do %>
    <!-- Custom right navigation -->
  <%% end %>
<%% end %>

<!-- Pattern 3: Complete override -->
<%%= rui :navigation, logo: content_tag(:span, "Brand") do %>
  <!-- Completely custom navigation structure -->
<%% end %>
<% end %>

